---
title: Mango Glazed Monkfish with Cavolo Nero and a Mint, Coriander and Yogurt Sauce
description: We love a good Mango Glazed Monkfish and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-spiced-monkfish-with-spiced-roast-potatoes-853fdf08-479a01af.jpg
